title: Elon Musk brings technology charm offensive to high tech tunnel plan
text:
Elon Musk brings technology charm offensive to high tech tunnel plan 1:32pm BST - 01:37
Billionaire entrepreneur Elon Musk is bringing his technology charm offensive to an attempt at digging a tunnel beneath part of Los Angeles to test designs for a high-speed subterranean transportation network he envisions for the city. Ryan Brooks reports ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
